Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:04.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Alien...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My duty is to observe Haruhi Suzumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:10.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and report all obtained data to the Integration Thought Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the task I have performed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.06,0:00:14.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...since I was born three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:17.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,During the past three years no uncertain elements appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation was extremely stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:21.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:23.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...an irregular factor which cannot go unheeded has appeared near Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:25.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:26.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From the perspective of the Data Integration Thought Entity...
