Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Integration Thought Entity carefully continued thorough observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:36.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:40.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We observed a data flare unlike any other witnessed on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion of data erupting from a region of a bow-shaped archipelago...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:46.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...instantly shrouded the planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and diffused into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At its center was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.59,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\be1\fs62\bord0\shad0\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(132,372)}Haruhi Suzumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:52.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Over the past three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:56.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a number of inquiries have been performed examining the existence known as Haruhi Suzumiya from all perspectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, her true identity remains unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:58.69,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx102\an1\be1\fs38\bord0\shad0\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(96,330)}Unexplainable explosion of data
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:01.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, a sector of the Integration Thought Entity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:01.86,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\be1\fs52\bord0\shad0\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(119,365)}Impossible to analyze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...believes that for humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and furthermore, us data life forms...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Haruhi Suzumiya is the key to our autoevolution...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and have thus commenced analysis accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They, as data life forms...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.12,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFF8F8&\pos(352,291)}Humans should only be able to handle a limited amount of information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...are unable to directly communicate with organic life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.87,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFF8F8&\pos(352,291)}yet a single one of those Terrestrial humans
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:17.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For they possess no language.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:21.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans lack the means to transmit ideas without words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:18.87,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFF8F8&\pos(352,291)}Intermittent torrents of data
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.38,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(352,291)}occur randomly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why human-purpose interfaces such as myself were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:23.88,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(352,391)\fsp10}Furthermore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:29.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Data Integration Thought Entity is able to come in contact with humans through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFFFFF&\fsp8\pos(352,215)}Haruhi Suzumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFFFFF&\fsp8\pos(352,291)}herself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\be1\fs20\bord0\shad0\alpha&H22&\1c&HFFFFFF&\fsp8\pos(352,366)}is unaware of this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:35.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi Suzumiya holds hidden potential for autoevolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:40.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It is likely that she possesses the ability to control data in her surrounding environment as she wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:44.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:46.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:49.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:52.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just pretend that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I believe you about all that data whatever and so on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:00.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you revealing your identity to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have been chosen by Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not Haruhi Suzumiya is aware of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...her consciousness has an effect on the environment in the form of unconditional data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a reason why you were chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:13.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Haruhi Suzumiya hold all potential within your grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:18.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:24.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I was, marveling at how the tight-lipped wonder had finally opened her mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and out came this winding freakish spiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:29.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never would have imagined she was some crazy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go tell Haruhi this story, she'll be overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:38.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite frankly, I don't understand any of this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:39.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:42.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A large sector of the Data Integration Thought Entity has recognized that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...if Haruhi Suzumiya becomes aware of her own value and ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:50.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is the potential for indeterminable risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We must observe the situation for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:53.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it possible that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll tell Haruhi everything I just heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't take the data you feed her seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:00.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:05.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not the only interface placed on Earth by the Data Integration Thought Entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A sector of the Data Integration Thought Entity overmind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...intends on initiating proactive activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:12.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and observing the resulting fluctuations in data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the key to Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When crisis approaches, you will be first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:21.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't take any more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:29.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Humanoid inter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...whatcha-ma-call-it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:37.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must have picked up those bizarre delusions from reading SF novels all alone in her apartment for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:39.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure she locks herself up in her shell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:41.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...never talking to anyone in her class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:44.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both her and Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ought to just enjoy their school life in a normal fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The long-awaited transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's amazing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:54.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell without even seeing the student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:05:59.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I already tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Survey says that a student who transfers in halfway through the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is practically guaranteed to be a mysterious transfer student!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:08.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when who and how was that statistic derived?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If mysterious transfer students can be guaranteed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...most of Japan would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and of course, she's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.57,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\be1\3a&H99\fs30\frz-15\frx-20\fry-15\fscy110\bord0.2\3c&H000000&\pos(583,234)}Literary Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I went to the clubroom after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I found that Asahina-san had gallantly recovered in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you were willing to come back to the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit hesitant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I suppose that I'm still concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:32.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get the feeling I heard her say something similar before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you concerned about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to take my place, Nagato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato, have you ever played Othello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:06:58.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The immediately useful transfer student who joined class 1-9 today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:05.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the brigade chief, Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:13.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are members #1, #2, and #3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And incidentally, you're the fourth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone get along now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no problem with joining, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...what does this club do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you just what activities the SOS Brigade engages in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:35.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Find aliens, time travelers, and espers....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:36.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and have fun with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:42.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could feel the entire world grinding to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:47.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although I was reminded of Haruhi's proclamation at the beginning of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.75,0:07:50.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as one would expect from Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did he just see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:57.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall join.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to have a pleasant experience with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello? You're going to accept that explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:08.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As I just transferred here, I'm sure I have much to learn from you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so feel free to teach me the ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:13.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The cute one over there is Mikuru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the glasses girl over here is Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:23.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, now we have five members!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally a full-fledged club!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:27.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:33.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time for the SOS Brigade to unveil itself to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, let's join together as one and give it our all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you mean by unveil?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Speaking of which, Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:42.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...are you really okay with being included as a member?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rolling along to after school the next day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to turn-ons, you can't forget about maids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Every school life story has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:03.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what kind of school life stories do you read...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a picture to remember this by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:06.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:08.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:09.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tilt the chin a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch the apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:12.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Bigger smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Take over as cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:19.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make you a little sexier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wha-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- It's fine! It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}How is this fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:25.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}I shouldn't be talking when I'm the one pressing the shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}And glasses on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}But what are these pictures going to be used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:41.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A lolita with shapely breasts in a maid outfit wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on wear these clothes when in the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:53.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all have fun with Mikuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:55.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:57.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of what will happen afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:00.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:01.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More like come help stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more of this and you'll be stepping on laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What laws!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:12.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We already took a bunch of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's commence the first SOS Brigade meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:23.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've done a lot to make it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We passed out flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we even made a homepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:30.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The celebrity of the SOS Brigade in this school has skyrocketed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:34.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first stage can be considered a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:35.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}How can you call emotionally scarring Asahina-san a huge success?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:37.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:42.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...not a single tale of mysterious happenings has reached our brigade's e-mail inbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and not a single student has come in for consultation regarding bizarre troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:49.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}That's because nobody has a clue as to what this club does yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}We didn't even find out until yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone once said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good things come to those who wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:57.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we live in the modern world now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to find the good for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if you have to dig through the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:02.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to go search!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:03.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysteries of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, seeking mysterious phenomena...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...we begin our tour de city-wide search.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\frx45\fry0\frz-38\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(501,266)}Bicycles / Motorcycles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:09.14,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\frx45\fry0\frz-37\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(590,315)}No Parking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:09.14,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\frx45\fry0\frz-38\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(501,266)}Bicycles{\alpha&HFF&} / Motor{\alpha&H99&}cycles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.30,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\frx45\fry0\frz-38\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(501,266)}Bicycles / Motorcycles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:09.22,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\frx45\fry0\frz-37\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(590,315)}No Pa{\alpha&HFF&}rking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.30,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15\frx45\fry0\frz-37\c&H050505&\alpha&H99&\bord0\shad0\pos(590,315)}No Parking
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:12.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Next Saturday."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Meet at 9 AM in front of Kitaguchi station."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:15.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"If you don't show, heads will roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heads roll, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really don't want to waste my day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:22.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:23.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was Haruhi's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Split into two groups and search the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:32.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If one group finds any mysterious phenomena, contact the other group through cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:33.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today might be my lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I get to go on a date with Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...treating everyone here is but a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:47.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:51.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.16,0:11:55.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This seriously isn't a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go off to play somewhere, I'll strangle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with those words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:03.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the Haruhi team went off to search the east side of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:06.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asahina-san and I were supposed to search the west side, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever walked around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone with a boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:25.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:28.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never gone out with someone before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:33.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you probably have guys asking you out all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:36.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not allowed to get involved with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:46.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:49.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After some stumbling over her words...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:56.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Asahina-san eventually caught herself and said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You might not believe me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:02.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not belong in this epoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I come from further into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:09.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you exactly when and which time plane I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:16.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fad(0,4000)}The information about the future that can be revealed to people in the past is severely restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:16.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fad(4000,0)}Time cannot be viewed as something that flows continuously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fad(0,3400)}...rather time is an accumulation of punctuated planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(183,0,0,0,2460,2780,2780)}Yes. Picture it as animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:22.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's actually moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(0,0,220,0,0,240,3500)}...but it's actually composed of a sequence of still frames.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(235,100,100,0,2900,2900,2900)}Breaks exist between one time and another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(100,00,32,0,1600,2100,2630)}Though their rate of occurrence is close to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:32.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(32,32,255,0,0,0,3400)}That is why time has no continuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:34.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,473)\fade(220,0,0,0,2870,4800,4800)}Time travel means moving in a three-dimensional direction across the accumulated time planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Being from the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:41.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...my presence on this time plane is similar to that of an extra picture added into a flip book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:47.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...a large timequake was detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago if you count from the current time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:54.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After arriving in the past to investigate the matter, we were shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we tried, we were unable to go any further back in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:04.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The conclusion was that a large time fault had appeared between time planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We only learned the possible reason recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:10.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently for the future I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And the reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:13.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:14.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:17.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We found her in the center of the time warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:21.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is classified information so I'm unable to explain any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we can be certain that Suzumiya-san was the one who sealed the path to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think Haruhi is capable of something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We also find it a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:35.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san is unaware that she was the origin of a timequake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:42.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sent to observe if any new time variations will appear near Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:43.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:49.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably don't believe any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:49.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the person chosen by Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The details are classified so I can't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:58.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you are probably an important person to Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:04.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Every action she performs has a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Nagato and Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:10.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are extremely similar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:15.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have expected Suzumiya-san to assemble us in such a precise fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what they are, Asahina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to Haruhi now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:26.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're from the future....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...you should know what's going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:30.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:33.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if I tell Haruhi everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:34.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough authority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you don't believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:49.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I heard something similar a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:52.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about suddenly telling you all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First an alien...  Now a time traveler shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:04.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If someone out there can hear all this and be like, "Okay, sure." and believe it all, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can trade places.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Asahina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:08.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we put this all on hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:14.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just set the matter of whether or not I believe you aside and put this on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But may I ask one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:22.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me your real age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's classified information.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:29.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After that, a call suddenly came from Haruhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and we were set to reassemble at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:32.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Results?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:33.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you even looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't just wandering around, Mikuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys even find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we ate lunch, Haruhi told us to split in two again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew unmarked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet in front of the station at four.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You better find something this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with that said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, we split up searching north and south.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're responsible for the south side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About what you said the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:12.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started to feel a little like I can believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:13.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you need to kill time with Nagato in tow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...this is the only place I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.39,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fry10\frz-0.5\fs36\be1\pos(285,184)}Central Library
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:22.40,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}[Escape From the School!]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what time it is now, you moron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:34.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You lazy dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.12,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\be1\fs16\shad0\bord0.2\frz22\frx-15\fry5\fscy110\c&H220000&\3c&H420000&\pos(294,495)}Haruhi Suzumiya
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.12,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\be1\fs16\shad0\bord0.2\fscy110\frx-15\fry10\frz22\c&H220000&\3c&H420000&\pos(371,407)}[Talking]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.12,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs16\shad0\bord0.2\fscy110\frx10\frz23\c&H220000&\3c&H420000&\pos(458,402)}9 sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:41.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to meet up at four?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:42.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your ass back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Within thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was when the struggle began.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:49.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to move Nagato, who when reading, is apparently rooted to the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I had to get her a library card so she could borrow the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ignoring the flood of calls from Haruhi during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, after yielding no results nor satisfaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and wasting time and money like some kind of a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...today's outdoor activity came to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:07.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as we were splitting up, Asahina-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening to what I had to say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:13.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she whispered into my ear, which wasn't a bad feeling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly were you doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you discover something interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're not careless enough to let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...find them in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after tomorrow, we'll have a review over today's behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with that, she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs13\be1\shad0\c&H6CE9D6&\3a&H00&\3c&H3D7F4D&\pos(344,49)}Your illegally parked bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.01,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fs15\be1\shad0\3a&H00&\3c&H5176B9&\pos(384,135)\c&H5B825D&}has been confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This has to be a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:41.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A new week begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've reached the point where the humidity of the rainy season...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...leaves us sweating early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:48.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oddly enough, Haruhi didn't show up until right before the bell rang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fan me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fan yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard the story "The Bluebird of Happiness" before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After spending the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:07.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...being showered from behind by Haruhi's depressing aura of displeasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:10.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like a field mouse sensing an impending bushfire...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:11.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I scurried to the safety of the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides, there was someone I wanted to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you also have something to tell me concerning Suzumiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The "also" would imply that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:27.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the other two ladies have already approached you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Suzumiya isn't an ordinary person, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes things quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you start by telling me your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:42.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As you may have suspected, I am an esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can think of me as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:49.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't intending on a sudden transfer to this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the situation had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:51.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:56.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have anticipated that the two of them would join forces with Haruhi Suzumiya so readily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:20:00.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll have another opportunity to delve into the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing is believing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I also have something I would like to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll just give you a summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Agency" I belong to includes a number of other espers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:15.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there are a number of agents planted in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And ever since our creation three years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have been observing Suzumiya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything began three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:24.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:27.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was when I discovered within me what could only be described as ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Haruhi have to do with what happened three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:35.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps this world is but a dream a certain being is seeing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:38.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what the higher-ups in the "Agency'' believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And because it is just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:47.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...creating and altering this world we call reality is but child's play for that being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:50.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And we know the name of the being who is capable of such acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have defined such a being...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:55.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...as God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:59.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've even got people calling you God now, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could espers such as ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:06.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and characters such as Mikuru Asahina and Yuki Nagato...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:10.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so coincidentally appear at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:13.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because Suzumiya-san wished for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it probably happened three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:19.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that Haruhi remade the world three years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than remade...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:25.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...perhaps we should say that the world began three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is but our theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:30.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So. What do you people intend to do with Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If this world loses the favor of God...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:39.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...it could simply be destroyed and recreated at whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:42.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to feel some attachment to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask Haruhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:49.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are those within the "Agency" who indeed advocate such a measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:52.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as diehards who seek to further stimulate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:57.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the majority is of the opinion that we should not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:01.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She has yet to realize her true potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:03.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case we are of the idea that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:07.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she would be better off not knowing and living out her life in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:10.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let sleeping gods lie, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:12.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you guys aren't the ones dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, of course, a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:18.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:23.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...right now, we are simply operating under the assumption of a worst case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a test then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:27.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were an esper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:29.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:32.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:34.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...reheat this cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:38.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My power cannot be so easily apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:42.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I usually hold no power at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:43.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A number of conditions must be met...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...before I can use my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:47.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.85,0:22:50.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure there will eventually be an opportunity to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:52.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to drag on so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.86,0:22:55.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll excuse myself for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:22:59.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:01.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The biggest mystery would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.81,0:23:05.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's bad form, I investigated a number of things concerning you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,..and I can assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:09.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:16.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:24.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to obediently follow Haruhi's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.52,0:23:31.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:34.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Haruhi never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:35.23,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\frz-12\1c&HFFFFFF&\pos(400,408)}CHIEF
